∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : CommSemiring R] {k n : ℕ} (a : Fin n → R),
  let s_k := Multiset.esymm (Multiset.map a Finset.univ.val) k
  let s_1 := Multiset.esymm (Multiset.map a Finset.univ.val) 1
  iSup (fun a => s_k / (s_1 ^ k)) = 1 / Nat.factorial k

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrder R] [inst_1 : CommSemiring R] (k : ℕ), 
  iSup (fun (s : Multiset R) => s.esymm k / (s.esymm 1) ^ k) = 1 / (Nat.factorial k)

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : CommSemiring R] {n k : ℕ} (s : Multiset R),
  iSup (fun (a : Multiset R) => Multiset.esymm a k / (Multiset.esymm a 1) ^ k) = 1 / Nat.factorial k

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] {n k : ℕ} {s : Multiset R},
  (iSup fun (a : Fin n → R) =>
    s.esymm k / (s.esymm 1) ^ k) = 1 / Nat.factorial k

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] {n k : ℕ} (s : Multiset R),
  iSup (fun a : Fin n → R => Multiset.esymm s k / Multiset.esymm s 1 ^ k) = 1 / Nat.factorial k

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : CommSemiring R] (n k : ℕ) (s : Multiset R),
  let a := s.esymm k / (s.esymm 1) ^ k
  in iSup (fun s => a) = (algebraMap ℕ R) (Nat.factorial k)⁻¹

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] (k : ℕ),
  iSup (fun (s : Multiset R) =>
      Multiset.esymm s k / (Multiset.esymm s 1) ^ k) = 1 / (Nat.factorial k)

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] (k : ℕ),
  iSup (fun (a : Finset R) => Multiset.esymm a.val k / Multiset.esymm a.val 1 ^ k) = 1 / Nat.factorial k

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : CommSemiring R] (k : ℕ),
  (iSup fun (s : Multiset R) =>
    Multiset.esymm s k / Multiset.esymm s 1 ^ k) = 1 / (Nat.factorial k)

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] {n k : ℕ} (s : Multiset R), 
  iSup (fun a => (Multiset.esymm s k) / (Multiset.esymm s 1) ^ k) = 1 / (Nat.factorial k)
